@startuml 05-self-evaluation
title Self-evaluation / fact-checking flow

start
:User question;
note right: Plain or HR-policy stuffed
:Generate answer;
note right: Ollama chat client
:Fact-check answer;
note right: bespoke-minicheck model

if (passes evaluation?) then (yes)
  :Return answer;
  note right: 200 OK
else (no)
  :Throw exception;
  note right: InvalidAnswerException
  :GlobalExceptionHandler;
  note right: 400 Bad Request
endif

stop

@enduml
